WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
It starts with a single thought...

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
spreading through minds like wildfire

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.267
Every conversation becomes transmission. Every memory, mutation.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.000
The idea doesn't need you to believe it

